"{\"uid\": \"theepochtimes.com-us-doping-dispute-over-chinese-swimmers-puts-us-olympic-hosting-at-risk-5693898\", \"text\": \"A doping dispute involving Chinese swimmers could derail the 2028 Summer Olympics in Los Angeles and the newly awarded 2034 Winter Olympics in Salt Lake City.  The dispute stems from the case of 23 Chinese swimmers who, months before the 2020 Tokyo Olympics, tested positive for trimetazidine, or TMZ, which is used to increase stamina and hasten recovery time.\"}"